{"tid":2333324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國新增576宗確診，最大海鮮市場出現群組爆發","createTime":"2020-12-20T10:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T10:06:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"45a87e319dcfb009d578653022de018b352245b8","tid":2333324,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566274-20201220.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566274-20201220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=ce8e6753\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566274-20201220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6d3770e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566274-20201220.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國新增576宗新型肺炎確診個案，位於西南部沙沒沙空府的全國最大的海鮮市場，出現群組爆發，有516人確診，大部分病例是來自緬甸的外地勞工，其中9成患者無徵狀。<br />\n<br />\n泰國政府已經宣布沙沒沙空府即日起至1月3日，對該地區進行封鎖和禁止旅遊，學校、體育場、遊樂場及商場需要關閉，以防止疫情進一步擴散。<br />\n<br />\n泰國累計4900多宗確診，60人死亡。"},{"pid":"32aa3059425db607d6fbf38d08246f629999aa56","tid":2333324,"uid":353080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f31ce1b8e2e3b94bd53ec657138f4bed98c7e8f","tid":2333324,"uid":2247,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"泰多人中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908e616f70fb8f00d68f4e9cc2fbbb3fdd0212ba","tid":2333324,"uid":380881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"陳師姐 陳師父<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}